程序包的使用

  • <Unnamed>使用的<Unnamed>中的类 
    类 说明
    CheckFine
    This class is used to check if the user has overused the scooter.
    CheckInput
    Check user's or administrator's input are in a correct form.
    CheckStationReport
    Check how many scooters in each station and how many scooters on the way.
    CheckWeeklyReport
    Check user's usage and create a txt file to save the user's usage.
    ParkingLot
    This class contains all the information of stations.
    ParkinglotIO
    This class contains basic input and output method for parkingLot.
    Student
    This class contains all the information of students.
    StudentIO
    This class contains basic input and output method for Student.
    UserGUI_SelectScooter
    This class is used to put images and set frames on the pick up or return page.
